Description:Verify Mox Ruby ({T}: Add {R}), Mox Emerald ({T}: Add {G}) and Mox Pearl ({T}: Add {W}) each tap for their printed single colour. The board has NO other red/green/white source, so casting Lightning Bolt ({R}) forces Mox Ruby, Giant Growth ({G}) forces Mox Emerald, and Disenchant ({1}{W}) consumes Mox Pearl's {W} (the Swamp pays the generic {1}). P2 has a Jalum Tome (artifact) as a Disenchant target.

